&lt;p&gt;Impiricus is looking for motivated, curious, and driven interns to join our team. This is a general application for our internship program - we welcome candidates interested in areas such as Marketing, Sales, Product, Engineering, Data Science, Operations, Clinical Strategy, People, and Finance. Rather than applying to one specific opening, you&#39;re applying to be considered for internship opportunities as they become available across the company. When a role that fits your background and interests opens up, our team will reach out to discuss next steps. This is a unique opportunity to gain hands-on experience at a fast-growing, AI-powered health-tech startup, work directly with experienced founders and leaders, and contribute to work that has a real impact on physicians and patients.&lt;/p&gt;
