&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Summary:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a high-output Proposal Specialist to join our sales team to support 350+ RFP responses to media agencies whose clients are pharmaceutical brand teams. The majority of these RFPs are managed during our busy season, which falls between July and December.&lt;/p&gt;
