&lt;li&gt;Populate and format pricing tables, product grids, and campaign summaries in Excel&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage an active queue of concurrent proposals under strict deadlines, particularly during the July–December peak season&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate with internal stakeholders (sales, strategy, customer success, data team, and marketing) to gather inputs needed to complete each response&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use AI tools to accelerate first drafts, tailor boilerplate content to brand-specific objectives, and speed up research on therapeutic areas or competitive positioning, while applying judgment to ensure accuracy, tone, and compliance before submission&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
